title: Unhealthy Kids & Living in the Middle
description:
Black or white?  What a painful place to live.  Jillian talks about how invaluable it is to see the word with an open mind.  Then it's call time where Jillian answers questions on fitness, nutrition, inspiration and overall wellness.
